    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你因誓言而被束缚去拯救你的未婚妻。你每个夜晚都要面对诅咒。吸血鬼扩散黑暗，世界流淌鲜血。生存依靠智慧和意志，而不是运气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Vow: Vampire’s Curse</strong> 是一款融合 Roguelike 元素的黑暗奇幻回合制战术游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/8ac94c115b21d28c22d826cd70794c52.poster.avif?t=1772476900\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/8ac94c115b21d28c22d826cd70794c52.webm?t=1772476900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/8ac94c115b21d28c22d826cd70794c52.mp4?t=1772476900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>血染的格子战斗</strong>：每一步都可能带来死亡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/0042577468f0fa5bdaa5ea11c7f792de.poster.avif?t=1772476900\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/0042577468f0fa5bdaa5ea11c7f792de.webm?t=1772476900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/0042577468f0fa5bdaa5ea11c7f792de.mp4?t=1772476900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卡组构建决定一切</strong>：玩家在夜幕降临前选择卡牌。卡组成为策略、生命线与诅咒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/e98cbf429328189af196f574e0f14f64.poster.avif?t=1772476900\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/e98cbf429328189af196f574e0f14f64.webm?t=1772476900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/e98cbf429328189af196f574e0f14f64.mp4?t=1772476900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>白天准备，黑夜战斗</strong>：玩家白天加固防御、调整战术。黑暗降临时，吸血鬼发动袭击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/fba7d0d388617e6db70aac003f3453a7.poster.avif?t=1772476900\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/fba7d0d388617e6db70aac003f3453a7.webm?t=1772476900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/fba7d0d388617e6db70aac003f3453a7.mp4?t=1772476900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无尽的诅咒</strong>：玩家不断游玩、解锁内容，深入吸血鬼深渊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/185ff4602394e8df40a438ea48b004d8.poster.avif?t=1772476900\" width=780 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/185ff4602394e8df40a438ea48b004d8.webm?t=1772476900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291450/extras/185ff4602394e8df40a438ea48b004d8.mp4?t=1772476900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>忍受循环，或成为其中一部分。</strong></p>",
